      "text": [
        " جِهَادُ الْمَرْأَةِ حُسْنُ التَّبَعُّلِ "
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "A number of our companions, from Sahl Bin Ziyad, from Ali Bin Hassan, from Musa Bin Bakr, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Ibrahim<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘Jihad of the wife is goodness with the husband’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "4. A number of our people have narrated from Sahl ibn Ziyad from Ali ibn Hassan from Musa ibn Bakr who has said the following: “Abu Ibrahim, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘Jihad (struggle for the cause of Allah) of a woman is her living a proper spousal life.’” "
        ]
      }
    }
